<title>USA: Ind. Bond Bank deal repriced, EVEREN raises yields.</title>
<headline>Ind. Bond Bank deal repriced, EVEREN raises yields.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>EVEREN Securities Inc. said Tuesday it repriced and restructured Indiana Bond Bank's $6.3 million deal, raising yields in several maturities but leaving the top yield in 2023 unchanged at 6.20 percent.</p>
